sentences: He performed the music of Ned Rorem's song cycle Songs of Sadness, and Romeo and Juliet at Merkin recital hall in Manhattan on April 24, 2005.
Jones' solo CDs include A Heart and an Open Road (Motéma Music, 2011), Pat Jones Band (1995), and the EP Mystery Prize (2004).
